Ranged =
Ranged only setups are sometimes preferred for simplicity, especially if players aren't as comfortable with a large amount of equipment swaps.

Upon entering the boss arena, if Muspah spawns in Melee form, it may save time to leave and re-enter to spend more time overall hitting Muspah's ranged form, which has lower ranged defence. Alternatively, with a [[Zaryte crossbow]], using a special attack with [[Ruby bolts (e)]] special on the first Melee phase can be beneficial.

Alternatively, some players prefer to use a [[Elder maul]], [[Dragon warhammer]], or [[Tonalztics of ralos]] special attack to reduce Muspah's defence and speed up kill times.
